W. R. JOHNSON, v. ELIA E. JOHNSON 34 So. (2nd) 563 March 5, 1948 Rehearing denied April 22, 1948.

January Term, 1948

En Banc *275S. M. Preacher and W. W. Flournoy, for appellant. A. L. Johnson, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The record and the briefs in this cause have been examined and the judgment appealed from is affirmed on authority of Jones v. Jones 119 Fla. 824, 161 So. 836.

Affirmed.

TERRELL, CHAPMAN, ADAMS, SEBRING and BARNS, JJ., concur. THOMAS, C. J., dissents.
